        },
        {
            "title": "A股窄幅   半日微升約0.1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股窄幅，半日微升，兩市成交合計10770.26億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日升2點或0.07%，今早開報3634，跌5點或0.14%，低見3625點，跌14點或0.38%，即反覆向上，最高見3645點，升6點或0.16%。成交4495.98億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日升15點或0.14%，今早開報11136，跌57點或0.19%，最低見11108，跌49點或0.44%，中段高見11178點，升21點或0.19%，半日成交6274.28億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日升2點或0.06%，報4117點，今早開報4019，跌5點或0.12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日升4點或0.21%，報2347點，今早開報2338，跌5點或0.21%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15159277-a%e8%82%a1%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%840-1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-08 11:50:34",
